<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.GetIncludeSeverity" Title="GetIncludeSeverity method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager">LogManager</PageRef> ->
    GetIncludeSeverity
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetIncludeSeverity</TypeRef> method returns the manager-level severity filter.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      This method is safe to call concurrently with logging and target registration.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[ILogger::SeverityFilter GetIncludeSeverity() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="SeverityFilter!cobalt.logging.ILogger.SeverityFilter">
        The current manager-level severity filter.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
